{"type": "article", "id": 8725, "title": "Adidas 腕表", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-21T06:59:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 3, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234939vwyrQsjEOG4KY7US.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tAdidas 今年经典 Superstar 强势回归，以 Superstar 为灵感，Adidas 推出了这一款 ADH 1969 限量版 Superstar 腕表。材料上选取了耐磨损的 316 不锈钢，配合橡胶。表面为金色，表盘印有鞋底经典的花纹。包装为鞋盒，也显得别具一格。目前腕表定价 479 欧元，全球限量 500 只，<a href=\"http://www.uebervart-shop.de/en/product/adidas-consortium-adh-1969-ltd-edition-superstar-watch-gold\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234938frEAV9uok8X2IJtU.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.72777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234938FHDRVdao2I4SgAM0.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.73333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}